# Multitenant security

**SSOT:** `../whatorder-vault/Projects/WhatOrder/ai-rules/security-multitenant.md` — read before editing.

**Critical:**
- Two boundaries: dashboard (Firestore rules) + bot (Admin SDK, no rules)
- Never trust `businessId` from message body or unvalidated client input
- Dashboard queries must scope to active `businessId`; include in `useEffect` deps
- Deploy Firestore rules when client access patterns change

Must-read spec: `../whatorder-vault/Projects/WhatOrder/specs/security-multitenant.md`
